<p class="ql-align-center">最喜欢的是这个隐藏的大玄机</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">藏在中岛后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>远看以为是一面白墙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201129/7fd80c58a2c64837968e47e107f4815c.png" max-width="600" /></p>
