<p class="ql-align-center">连碗具餐具都按照颜色之分</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">分成了两个抽屉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201129/bec7477647cb4c6ba8243ad423225de6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再来看看这个通透敞亮的LDK一体空间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">柠檬精再次留下了没有技术含量的泪水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201129/29f0b50c475c4e189eecfd7e5e4d35fe.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201129/2ad6b0e29d4840bb9546c100f84ebfa1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>最后来看看卧室</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">房间都在二楼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从电视机旁边的小楼梯上去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>瞬间有一种被102㎡欺骗了的感觉！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>原来是两层！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201129/e19796910230484e91433d0b74422d35.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>&lt;休闲区&gt;</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">房间大的任性真是说来就来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">上到二楼后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">首先映入眼帘的不是硕大的卧室</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>而是...单独竟然有一个休闲区！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201129/7f47b0d16dcf49ed929f9428e04bd91f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就两只懒人沙发</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个小收纳柜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>窝在这里打打游戏聊聊天</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>朋友聚会倒是real方便</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201129/36ae08597c0347f796a7583beefe94a1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从楼上向下望</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">完整的楼下风景尽收眼帘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201129/77cae3ac6f194d99aac2753634ea7813.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这令人哭泣的层高</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了羡慕还是羡慕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201129/d9a626cbaf644462b42a5aa06beefb70.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>&lt;儿童房&gt;</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两个单独的房间其中之一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是这间儿童房</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201129/e3e9a8d1f5664fe38d8bd06e50974d57.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">MUJI的落地衣架上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">挂满了小朋友的衣物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201129/59e40ce921f9450a953ef306fb8d5b27.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">旁边还有一架书桌和电脑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孩子长大了也能在这学习</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201129/038a931ff6a74856a34187b79d42cc8b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>&lt;主卧&gt;</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实卧室面积都不大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">主卧面积也没有想象中大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201129/6b1d82b352f44f35961227849c21bd5d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">左侧有一个小阳台，右侧是小衣帽间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（不过没有更多镜头了，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只能看到角落里的收纳箱）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201129/e64c4c2bdae24269a0667525eebaf0fb.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">最后还问到了屋主全屋最喜欢的地方。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>屋主说，是客厅的大落地窗。</strong>窗户恰巧另一边绿树成荫，景色非常好。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">谁不喜欢呢~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201129/ab21a27e313e4923b366b3d18507f55e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">而当我看到房子的外景后，我再次留下了两行没有技术含量的泪水。</p>
